			 * is specified.
			 *
			 * @alias sap.ui.table.TableUtils.CellInfo#isOfType
			 * @param {int} cellTypeMask Bitmask of cell types to check.
			 * @returns {boolean} Whether the specified cell type mask matches the type of the cell.
